# init()

**Initializer**

Creates a per-minute update schedule.

## Declaration

```swift
init()
```

## Discussion

Use the [doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/EveryMinuteTimelineSchedule/entries(from:mode:)] method to get the sequence of dates.
